sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as "Client Application"
    participant F as "Follower SR Node"
    participant L as "Primary SR Node (Crashes)"
    participant K as "Kafka KRaft Coordinator"
    
    App->>F: POST /subjects/users-value/versions (Register request)
    F->>L: Forward write request to Primary
    Note over L: Primary Node Crashes / Network Partition
    F-->>F: Forward request times out after kafkastore.timeout.ms
    
    %% Election
    F->>K: Heartbeat lost / Initiate new leader election
    K->>K: Select Node 1 (Follower) as new Primary
    K-->>F: Elect Node 1 as Primary (Promoted)
    
    %% Re-route
    App->>F: Retry write request
    Note over F: Node 1 is now Primary. Handles write locally.
    F->>K: Publish schema to _schemas topic
    F-->>App: Return Schema ID (Registration Successful)
